{"tid":921062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨入營演習 非暴力抗爭佔中","createTime":"2018-11-29T09:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T11:33:44.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c076d299ba45daeac7ec8e14480a9cc59134de4a","tid":921062,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:36:12.000Z","msg":"本港爭取普選的和平佔中運動昨日亦舉行首場非暴力抗爭演習，模擬不同場景，如警察出動警棍、胡椒噴霧、水炮鎮壓，教導近100名佔中糾察義工可以如何應對。佔中發起人之一的戴耀廷指出，抗爭演習是要向參與者灌輸不要以暴易暴，和平佔中會吸取台灣太陽花學運的經驗，以豐富佔中準備。<br />\n記者：謝明明<br />\n<br />\n和平佔中首場非暴力演練於昨午在金鐘添馬公園舉行，約100名簽署了佔中意向書的市民參加，他們戴上寫有「和平佔中」的藍色頭巾及獲發一本非暴力抗爭手冊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20140331/large/a0401c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140331%2Flarge%2Fa0401c.gif&h=fb63ab04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20140331/large/31la2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140331%2Flarge%2F31la2p2.jpg&h=6d0de13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20140830/photo/bkn-20140830092743581-0830_00822_001_01p.jpg?20140831051817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20140830092743581-0830_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20140831051817&h=40e42145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20140330/large/1396167207_ccea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140330%2Flarge%2F1396167207_ccea.jpg&h=326ee33b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1256/640pixfolder/N1256_139_p1_2a_FAI_0314_9692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FN